en.title: Samboy Lim (Skywalker) Doing Demonsrations At The NBI (National Bureau of Investigation).
en.content:
FE is growing leaps and bounds in the Philippines! Photo show FE’s Philippines Spokesman, Basketball Legend, Samboy Lim (Skywalker) doing demonstrations at the NBI (National Bureau of Investigation). 
Cellular Phone Test: Explaining the negative effect of 
e-smog (emf) on us and how it destabilize our 
natural bio field.
Flexibility Test: A vast difference of 12-14 inches.
Strength Test: Dramatic increase of strength and 
balance for Atty. Angelito Magno 
(Chief of Special Action Unit).
L to R : (DFA Special Agent) Napoleon, Samboy Lim, 
Atty. Victor Bessat 
(Deputy Director of Special Investigation Services)
and Jeremy.
